Hif'il: The _hif'il_ (הִפְעִיל) is one of the [[Hebrew binyanim]]. ([[{{Binyan}} is a special concept in Hebrew and Aramaic grammar]].)
- Verbs in the _hif'il_ have the properties of being [[active]] and [[causative]].
- The _hif'il_ corresponds to the [[_af'el_]] in Aramaic.
- The _hif'il_ [[has various verb {{forms}}]].

- הרחיק

